    "繧ｳ繝ｳ繝斐Η繝ｼ繧ｿ繧ｷ繧ｹ繝・Β繝ｻ讒区・隕∫ｴ": { chapter: "隨ｬ2遶", title: "隨ｬ2遶 菫｡諱ｯ螳牙・謚譛ｯ" },
    "繝・・繧ｿ繝吶・繧ｹ": { chapter: "隨ｬ2遶", title: "隨ｬ2遶 菫｡諱ｯ螳牙・謚譛ｯ" },
    "繝阪ャ繝医Ρ繝ｼ繧ｯ": { chapter: "隨ｬ2遶", title: "隨ｬ2遶 菫｡諱ｯ螳牙・謚譛ｯ" },
    "繧ｻ繧ｭ繝･繝ｪ繝・ぅ": { chapter: "隨ｬ1遶", title: "隨ｬ1遶 莉荵域弍菫｡諱ｯ螳牙・ / 隨ｬ2遶 菫｡諱ｯ螳牙・謚譛ｯ" }
  }
};

function renderCbtHeatmap() {
  const container = document.getElementById("cbt-heatmap-grid");
  if (!container) return;
  
  const history = loadCbtHistory();
  
  // Aggregate stats per category
  const categories = [
    "莨∵･ｭ豢ｻ蜍輔・邨悟霧謌ｦ逡･",
    "豕募漁繝ｻ讓呎ｺ門喧",
    "繧ｷ繧ｹ繝・Β謌ｦ逡･繝ｻ莨∫判",
    "繧ｷ繧ｹ繝・Β髢狗匱謚陦・,
    "繝励Ο繧ｸ繧ｧ繧ｯ繝医・繝阪ず繝｡繝ｳ繝・,
    "繧ｵ繝ｼ繝薙せ繝槭ロ繧ｸ繝｡繝ｳ繝医・逶｣譟ｻ",
    "蝓ｺ遉守炊隲悶・繧｢繝ｫ繧ｴ繝ｪ繧ｺ繝",
    "繧ｳ繝ｳ繝斐Η繝ｼ繧ｿ繧ｷ繧ｹ繝・Β繝ｻ讒区・隕∫ｴ",
    "繝・・繧ｿ繝吶・繧ｹ",
    "繝阪ャ繝医Ρ繝ｼ繧ｯ",
    "繧ｻ繧ｭ繝･繝ｪ繝・ぅ"
  ];
  
  const stats = {};
  categories.forEach(cat => {
    stats[cat] = { total: 0, correct: 0 };
  });
  
  // Calculate stats from history
  history.forEach(item => {
    if (stats[item.category]) {
      stats[item.category].total += 1;
      if (item.isCorrect) stats[item.category].correct += 1;
    }
  });
  
  let html = "";
  categories.forEach(cat => {
    const data = stats[cat];
    const rate = data.total > 0 ? Math.round((data.correct / data.total) * 100) : null;
    
    let stateClass = "cell-no-data";
    let displayRate = "N/A";
    
    if (rate !== null) {
      displayRate = `${rate}%`;
      if (rate < 60) {
        stateClass = "cell-low";
      } else if (rate < 80) {
        stateClass = "cell-medium";
      } else {
        stateClass = "cell-high";
      }
    }
    
    let displayName = cat;
    if (displayName.length > 8) displayName = displayName.slice(0, 7) + "..";
    
    html += `
      <div class="heatmap-cell ${stateClass}" onclick="selectHeatmapCell('${cat}', ${data.total}, ${data.correct}, ${rate})">
        <div class="heatmap-cell-title" title="${cat}">${displayName}</div>
        <div class="heatmap-cell-rate">${displayRate}</div>
      </div>
    `;
  });
  
  container.innerHTML = html;
  
  const recCard = document.getElementById("cbt-heatmap-recommendation-card");
  if (recCard) recCard.style.display = "none";
}

function selectHeatmapCell(category, total, correct, rate) {
  const recCard = document.getElementById("cbt-heatmap-recommendation-card");
  if (!recCard) return;
  
  recCard.style.display = "flex";
  
  const nameEl = document.getElementById("rec-category-name");
  nameEl.innerHTML = `<i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i> 遏･隸・せ蛻・ｱｻ: ${category}`;
  
  const statsEl = document.getElementById("rec-category-stats");
  if (total === 0) {
    statsEl.innerText = "遲秘｢倩ｮｰ蠖・ 證よ裏蛛夐｢俶焚謐ｮ縲りｯｷ蜈亥盾蜉 CBT 讓｡諡滓ｵ玖ｯ包ｼ・;
  } else {
    statsEl.innerText = `遲秘｢俶ュ蜀ｵ: 蜈ｱ蛛夐｢・${total} 驕・| 遲泌ｯｹ ${correct} 驕・| 豁｣遑ｮ邇・${rate}%`;
  }
  
  const adviceEl = document.getElementById("rec-advice-box");
  
  if (total === 0) {
    adviceEl.style.background = "rgba(255,255,255,0.03)";
    adviceEl.style.borderColor = "rgba(255,255,255,0.1)";
    adviceEl.style.color = "var(--text-muted)";
    adviceEl.innerHTML = "謠千､ｺ: 豐｡譛芽ｶｳ螟溽噪扈溯ｮ｡謨ｰ謐ｮ・梧嘯譌ｶ譌豕慕ｻ吝・陦･荵謗ｨ闕舌・;
    return;
  }
  
  const mapping = KNOWLEDGE_LECTURE_MAPPING[currentSubject];
  const targetChapter = (mapping && mapping[category]) ? mapping[category] : null;
  
  if (rate >= 80) {
    adviceEl.style.background = "rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.08)";
    adviceEl.style.borderColor = "rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15)";
    adviceEl.style.color = "#a7f3d0";
    adviceEl.innerHTML = `
      <span>総 謔ｨ逧・詞謠｡蠎ｦ髱槫ｸｸ莨倡ｧ・∫ｻｧ扈ｭ菫晄戟・・/span>
    `;
  } else {
    const isRed = rate < 60;
    adviceEl.style.background = isRed ? "rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.08)" : "rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08)";
    adviceEl.style.borderColor = isRed ? "rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15)" : "rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15)";
    adviceEl.style.color = isRed ? "#fca5a5" : "#fde047";
    
    if (targetChapter) {
      adviceEl.innerHTML = `
        <span>笞・・隸･蛻・ｱｻ謗梧升蠎ｦ霎・ｼｱ・悟ｼｺ辜亥ｻｺ隶ｮ陦･荵莉･荳玖ｮｲ荵臥ｫ闃ゑｼ・/span>
        <button class="rec-link" onclick="redirectToChapter('${currentSubject}', '${targetChapter.chapter}')">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-to-bracket"></i> 荳髞ｮ霍ｳ霓ｬ蛻ｰ: ${targetChapter.title}
        </button>
      `;
    } else {
      adviceEl.innerHTML = `
        <span>笞・・謔ｨ逧・詞謠｡蠎ｦ髴隕∝刈蠑ｺ・悟ｻｺ隶ｮ螟堺ｹ逶ｸ蜈ｳ隸ｾ遞玖ｮｲ荵会ｼ・/span>
      `;
    }
  }
}

function redirectToChapter(subject, chapterNumStr) {
  let lessons = [];
  if (subject === 'itpass') {
    lessons = IT_PASSPORT_LESSONS;
  } else if (subject === 'sg') {
    lessons = (typeof SG_LESSONS !== 'undefined') ? SG_LESSONS : [];
  }
  
  const target = lessons.find(l => l.chapterName && l.chapterName.includes(chapterNumStr));
  if (target) {
    switchSubject(subject);
    
    if (subject === 'itpass') {
      switchItPassSubMode('lessons');
      loadItPassLesson(target.id);
    } else if (subject === 'sg') {
      switchSgSubMode('lessons');
      loadSgLesson(target.id);
    }
    
    const cbtContainer = document.getElementById("cbt-exam-container");
    if (cbtContainer) cbtContainer.style.display = "none";
    
    showToast(`当 蟾ｲ荳ｺ謔ｨ閾ｪ蜉ｨ霍ｳ霓ｬ蛻ｰ・・{target.chapterName} - ${target.titleZh}`, "success");
  } else {
    showToast("笞・・譛ｪ謇ｾ蛻ｰ蟇ｹ蠎皮噪隶ｲ荵臥ｫ闃ゑｼ・, "error");
  }
}


